ja|足利義満|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に叛し堺で挙兵 * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1861|ja|1861|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - 種痘所を西洋医学所に改称し西洋医学の教育機関に改組。{{ill|University of Tokyo|ja|東京大学|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 医学部の前身 * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Iwanashi Prefecture|ja|岩鼻県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が合併し{{ill|Gunma Prefecture|ja|群馬県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に。群馬県の現在の県域が確定
== Births == * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1860|ja|1860|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Jigoro Kano|ja|嘉納治五郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Judo|ja|柔道|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 家（+ {{ill|1938|ja|1938|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1596|ja|1596|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 17|ja|12月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Sakai Tadaatsu|ja|酒井忠次|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、{{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings|ja|徳川四天王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の一人（* {{ill|1527|ja|1527|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
