{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Enkang (Han)|ja|延康 (漢)|lt=Enkang|lt_ja=延康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Huangchu|ja|黄初|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|220|ja|220|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の献帝が、{{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} の子・{{ill|Cao Pi|ja|曹丕|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に玉璽と綬を譲る。{{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|lt=Han|lt_ja=漢|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が滅亡し{{ill|Wei (Three Kingdoms)|ja|魏 (三国)|lt=Wei|lt_ja=魏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が成立 * {{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1154|ja|1154|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ninpei|ja|仁平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} から{{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に{{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year /{{ill|Genchū|ja|元中|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1392|ja|1392|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Nanboku-chō period (Japan)|ja|南北朝時代 (日本)|lt=Nanboku-chō|lt_ja=南北朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 合一により、南朝の{{ill|Emperor Go-Kameyama|ja|後亀山天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が吉野から京都へ出発 * {{ill|Ōei|ja|Ōei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1399|ja|1399|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ōei Rebellion|ja|Ōeiの乱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が始まる。{{ill|Ōuchi Yoshihiro|ja|大内義弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が{{ill|Ashikaga Yoshimitsu|ja|足利義満|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に叛し堺で挙兵 * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1861|ja|1861|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - 種痘所を西洋医学所に改称し西洋医学の教育機関に改組。{{ill|University of Tokyo|ja|東京大学|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 医学部の前身 * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ・{{ill|Iwanashi Prefecture|ja|岩鼻県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が合併し{{ill|Gunma Prefecture|ja|群馬県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} に。群馬県の現在の県域が確定
