{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月廿八|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 28일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Enkang (Han)|ja|延康 (漢)|lt=Enkang|lt_ja=延康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Huangchu|ja|黄初|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|220|ja|220|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} の献帝が、{{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} の子・{{ill|Cao Pi|ja|曹丕|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} に玉璽と綬を譲る。{{ill|Later Han|ja|後漢|lt=Han|lt_ja=漢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が滅亡し{{ill|Wei (Three Kingdoms)|ja|魏 (三国)|lt=Wei|lt_ja=魏|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が成立 * {{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1154|ja|1154|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ninpei|ja|仁平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} から{{ill|Kyushu|ja|久寿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} に{{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Meitoku|ja|明徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year /{{ill|Genchū|ja|元中|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 9th year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1392|ja|1392|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Nanboku-chō period (Japan)|ja|南北朝時代 (日本)|lt=Nanboku-chō|lt_ja=南北朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 合一により、南朝の{{ill|Emperor Go-Kameyama|ja|後亀山天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が吉野から京都へ出発 * {{ill|Ōei|ja|Ōei|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year ([[Julian calendar]] {{ill|1399|ja|1399|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ōei Rebellion|ja|Ōeiの乱|1=Ōei Rebellion|2=ja|3=応永の乱|4=zh|5=应永之乱|6=ko|7=오에이의 난|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が始まる。{{ill|Ōuchi Yoshihiro|ja|大内義弘|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が{{ill|Ashikaga Yoshimitsu|ja|足利義満|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} に叛し堺で挙兵 * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1861|ja|1861|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - 種痘所を西洋医学所に改称し西洋医学の教育機関に改組。{{ill|University of Tokyo|ja|東京大学|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 医学部の前身 * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Iwanashi Prefecture|ja|岩鼻県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} が合併し{{ill|Gunma Prefecture|ja|群馬県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} に。群馬県の現在の県域が確定
== Births == * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Jigoro Kano|ja|嘉納治五郎|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Judo|ja|柔道|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 家（+ {{ill|1938|ja|1938|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1596|ja|1596|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 17|ja|12月17日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） - {{ill|Sakai Tadaatsu|ja|酒井忠次|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 、{{ill|Military commander|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ・{{ill|Tokugawa Four Heavenly Kings|ja|徳川四天王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} の一人（* {{ill|1527|ja|1527|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ）
