 of Tokyo|University of Tokyo]] 医学部の前身 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shichinichiichi Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Obata Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isesaki Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annaka Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Numata Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takasaki Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maebashi Prefecture|qq=}} ・{{ill|Iwanashi Prefecture|ja|岩鼻県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwanashi Prefecture|qq=}} が合併し[[:en:Gunma Prefecture|Gunma Prefecture]] に。群馬県の現在の県域が確定
