orian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1861|ja|1861|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1861|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 30|November 30]] ） - 種痘所を西洋医学所に改称し西洋医学の教育機関に改組。[[:en:University of Tokyo|University of Tokyo]] 医学部の前身 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1000}} [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shichinichiichi Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 七日市藩}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Obata Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 小幡藩}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isesaki Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 伊勢崎藩}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annaka Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安中藩}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Numata Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 沼田藩}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takasaki Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 高崎藩}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maebashi Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 前橋藩}} ・{{ill|Iwanashi Prefecture|ja|岩鼻県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwanashi Prefecture|qq=}} が合併し[[:en:Gunma Prefecture|Gunma Prefecture]] に。群馬県の現在の県域が確定
