== Events == * {{ill|Enkang (Han)|ja|延康 (漢)|lt=Enkang|lt_ja=延康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkang (Han)|qq=|1=Yankang|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q8011911}} 1st year/{{ill|Huangchu|ja|黄初|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Huangchu|qq=|1=Huangchu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q840256}} 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:220|220]] [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ） - [[:en:Han_dynasty#Eastern_Han|Later Han]]{{citation needed|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Han|qq=}} の献帝が、[[:en:Cao Cao|Cao Cao]] の子・[[:en:Cao Pi|Cao Pi]] に玉璽と綬を譲る。[[:en:Han_dynasty#Eastern_Han|Later Han]]{{citation needed|lt=Han|lt_ja=漢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Han|qq=}} が滅亡し[[:en:Cao Wei|Wei]] が成立 * [[:en:Kyūju|Kyushu]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1154|1154]] [[:en:December 4|December 4]] ） - [[:en:Ninpei|Ninpei]] から[[:en:Kyūju|Kyushu]] に{{ill|Change of era|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Change of era|qq=|1=era change|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11498853}} * [[:en:Meitoku|Meitoku]] 3rd year /[[:en:Genchū|Genchū]] 9th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1392|1392]] [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ） - [[:en:Nanboku-chō period|Nanboku-chō]] 合一により、南朝の[[:en:Emperor Go-Kameyama|Emperor Go-Kameyama]] が吉野から京都へ出発 * [[Ōei]]{{efn|July 1394 through April 1428|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 6th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1399|1399]] [[:en:November 26|November 26]] ） - {{ill|Ōei Rebellion|ja|Ōeiの乱|1=Ōei Rebellion|2=ja|3=応永の乱|4=zh|5=应永之乱|6=ko|7=오에이의 난|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Rebellion|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōei Rebellion|qq=|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10285774}} が始まる。[[:en:Ōuchi Yoshihiro|Ōuchi Yoshihiro]] が[[:en:Ashikaga Yoshimitsu|Ashikaga Yoshimitsu]] に叛し堺で挙兵 * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1861|1861]] [[:en:November 30|November 30]] ） - 種痘所を西洋医学所に改称し西洋医学の教育機関に改組。[[:en:University of Tokyo|University of Tokyo]] 医学部の前身 * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1871|1871]] [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ） - {{ill|Shichinichiichi Prefecture|ja|七日市県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shichinichiichi Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 七日市藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 七日市藩|1=Nanokaichi Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q3034506}} ・{{ill|Obata Prefecture|ja|小幡県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Obata Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 小幡藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 小幡藩|1=Obata Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q3034394}} ・{{ill|Isesaki Prefecture|ja|伊勢崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Isesaki Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 伊勢崎藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 伊勢崎藩|1=Isesaki Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10863241}} ・{{ill|Annaka Prefecture|ja|安中県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annaka Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安中藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安中藩|1=Annaka Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1004324}} ・{{ill|Numata Prefecture|ja|沼田県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Numata Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 沼田藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 沼田藩|1=Numata Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10863454}} ・{{ill|Takasaki Prefecture|ja|高崎県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takasaki Prefecture|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 高崎藩|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 高崎藩|1=Takasaki Domain|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10863413}} ・{{ill|Maebashi Prefecture|ja|前橋県|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maebashi Prefecture|qq=|ja_